  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'MANUAL

    Welcome to your new intergalactic travel agency! Your ultimate
    goal is to manage the office

    and survive for as many working days as possible.
    To do this, you will need to welcome

    alien clients, understand their requests,
    and send them to the right destination before time

    runs out. Pay close attention
    to the budget: if your balance drops to zero or below due to

    expenses, the
    agency will go bankrupt.

'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
