      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '

    Investigation Phase: This is the most important operation. You must
    cross-reference

    the text of the client''s request with the fixed rules written
    in this Manual and with the

    variable events reported in the daily News.
    Only by combining these three elements will

    you be able to deduce the perfect
    planet.


    Finding the Symbol: Once you have identified the ideal destination,
    consult the

    company Brochures to find the unique identifying symbol associated
    with that planet.


    Stamping: Insert the alien''s ticket into the stamping
    machine. Select the symbol you just

    found and firmly apply it to the document.'
